Preamble

This licence agreement is based on the CERN Open Hardware Licence Version 2 - Weakly Reciprocal, which is a copyleft hardware license. It is designed to promote collaboration and sharing in the field of open hardware design.

Licence Scope

This licence applies to the hardware designs, specifications, and related documentation in this repository, including but not limited to CAD files, schematics, and firmware code.

Permissions

Subject to the conditions below, you may copy, modify, and redistribute this hardware design.

Conditions

1. You must retain this licence with all copies and modifications of this design.

2. If you make modifications to this design, you must make those modifications available under the same licence.

3. If you use this design in a product, you must make the design files for that product available under the same licence.

4. You must include a notice in any product that uses this design, stating that it is based on this open hardware design.

